{
 "name": "RPlog_Return_of_a_Jedi_Part_II",
 "title": "Return of a Jedi (Part II)",
 "summary": "As the reunion deepens, the dark adept Simon Sezirok confronts the grief-stricken Mira in a public hall, declaring himself a true Selas of honor and dedication, more than mere words despite the darkness in him. Mira, stunned and weeping, finally admits that she abandoned him -- a betrayal that wounds her more than his fallen state -- and apologizes, confessing that she misses him. Unable to bear that her presence only worsens things, Mira turns and walks away, resolving to one day make it up to Simon, the scarred Morganna a watchful presence. The emotional reckoning lays bare the broken bond between teacher and lost student.",
